title: Sunken Temple of the Golden Knight
story: Long after the Golden Knight's defeat the temple remained abandoned. Recently a band of goblins rediscovered it, making it their center of operation.

notes.text: A great gate with a keyhole to the west.
An exotic katana, a scarf and a lamp in a chest.
A rear entrance into the temple. A dying elf, a key among his belongings.
A sculpture of an elf rogue, a mysterious, vibrating skull in its hands.
